### =============================================================================
### SmartHaus — Ubiquiti Demo Requests
### =============================================================================
###
### Test requests for the Ubiquiti UniFi Protect webhook endpoints running in
### the demo Docker Compose stack (docker-compose.demo.yml).
###
### Usage:
###   1. Start the demo: docker compose -f docker-compose.demo.yml up --build
###   2. Wait for the smarthaus service to become healthy
###   3. Run these requests from VS Code (REST Client extension)
### =============================================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/v1.0/ubiquiti

### ---------- Motion Detection ----------

### Simulate a motion detection event from a front door camera
POST {{baseUrl}}/event/motion?camera_id=abc123&camera_name=FrontDoor

### ---------- Smart Detection ----------

### Simulate a person detected at the front door (high confidence)
POST {{baseUrl}}/event/smart?type=person&camera_id=abc123&camera_name=FrontDoor&score=0.95

### Simulate a vehicle detected in the driveway
POST {{baseUrl}}/event/smart?type=vehicle&camera_id=def456&camera_name=Driveway&score=0.88

### Simulate an animal detected in the garden
POST {{baseUrl}}/event/smart?type=animal&camera_id=ghi789&camera_name=Garden&score=0.72

### Simulate a package detected at the front door
POST {{baseUrl}}/event/smart?type=package&camera_id=abc123&camera_name=FrontDoor&score=0.91

### ---------- Doorbell Ring ----------

### Simulate a doorbell ring event
POST {{baseUrl}}/event/ring?camera_id=abc123&camera_name=FrontDoor

### ---------- Query ----------

### Get the current Ubiquiti event snapshot (aggregated counts and timestamps).
### Note: This endpoint requires authentication (Basic auth or configured scheme).
GET {{baseUrl}}
